Goldman Sachs May Give Opinion May 12 on Lactalis Bid, Sole Says

-- B y   F r a n c e s c a   C i n e l l i
-- 
2011-05-07T11:14:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-07/goldman-sachs-may-give-opinion-may-12-on-lactalis-bid-sole-says.html
Goldman Sachs Group Inc. may present
its fairness opinion May 12 on Groupe Lactalis’s 3.4 billion-
euro ($4.9 billion) bid for  Parmalat SpA (PLT) ,  Il Sole 24 Ore 
reported without saying where it got the information.  Parmalat Chief Executive Officer Enrico Bondi may have
asked lawyer Giuseppe Lombardi, who advices the company, as well
as Shearman & Sterling and Studio Legale Legance to go through
Lactalis’s prospectus, which isn’t yet public, the newspaper
reported.  Parmalat’s board meeting is scheduled on May 12 to approve
quarterly results.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Francesca Cinelli in Milan at 
 fcinelli@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Ludden at 
 jludden@bloomberg.net  